    <p class="bold mt0 mb0">Important info about PayPal and Giving Fund:</p>
  </div>
  <ul class="mt1 mb2">
    <li><strong>Notify us when you deposit with PayPal</strong>—we can't fund your account without you reaching out.</li>
    <li>PayPal will charge an additional variable fee of around 4% or more, on top of the 7% Bank fee.</li>
  </ul>
  <div class="border-top card__banner card__darker secondary">
    <strong class="warning">Questions?</strong> 
      <span>Contact the Bank team at <a href="mailto:bank@hackclub.com">bank@hackclub.com</a></span>
